      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOTORIOUS BLAZE (8) box seated early before forging to the lead turning and lifting to score (22.45) at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 390m. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Looks the testing material. JACAERYS BALE (1) showed strong pace early from the inside rail and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing fourth over 390m this track in 22.66. Expected to feature in the finish. COSMIC REWARD (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (24.52) at Bendigo behind Lainey Jane in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Has a solid record from this box including three wins and a minor placing. Leading chance. BROOMBRAE FRITZ (6) can sneak into the finish.",
